I"ß<h3 id="record-100-sessions">Record 100% Sessions</h3>

<p>Get the complete picture of your users experience with user based 100% session recordings. View errors, dead clicks, UTM tags, location and much more.</p>

<h3 id="view-user-based-activity">View User Based Activity</h3>

<p>Get insights into all sessions for a user. View all events, locations and devices used to access your site. Identify sessions and click to view any recording.</p>

<h3 id="user-behavior-patterns">User Behavior Patterns</h3>

<p>Understand where your users are coming from (source), pages visited and duration of each return visit by user. Giving you control over your user data and everything you need to understand your customer better.</p>

<h3 id="identify-and-solve-customer-struggles">Identify and Solve Customer Struggles</h3>

<p>Search and filter your user sessions using Natural Language Search. Type in exactly what you are looking for and get to understanding your customers struggles faster.</p>
